  "id": "La4e8zkH",
  "slug": "simple-weapons-for-better-combat",
  "title": "Simple Weapons for Better Combat",
  "description": "Adds vanilla-like weapons designed and balanced around the better combat mod",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod simply adds more weapon types that fit in with vanilla. This mod focuses on quality over quantity and <del>doesn't add a lot of weapons</del>, however every weapon brings something new to the table. This mod currently includes 8 new weapons, 7 with special abilities. * Special abilities can be disabled in the config</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">These weapons are balanced around the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-combat-by-daedelus\">Better Combat</a> mod, however you can use this mod without it.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If you've played the mod before and want to help with balancing, please fill out this short poll. (Thank you)</p>\n<p>https://forms.gle/xzawb9UWQXDse59u9</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Weapons</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Scythe:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KeikcPj.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: Medium</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Slow</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: Very High&nbsp; *Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Inflicts Bleed, dealing damage over time, higher tiers inflict bleed for longer</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Greatsword:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JBhp5oz.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: High</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Slow</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: High&nbsp; *Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Spear:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/idYcdKW.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: Very High</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Very Slow</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: Very High&nbsp; *Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Cavalry: Increases damage while mounted</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Dagger:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iJuHMWb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: Very Low</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Very High</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: Very Low&nbsp; *Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Backstab: Increases damage and staggers unaware entities</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Deals less knockback</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Katar:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BKEh0SD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: Medium-High</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Slow-Medium</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: Very Low&nbsp; *Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Has lifesteal, which is based on amount of enemies hit rather than damage dealt</span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Scimitar:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h0b8SbV.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: Low-Medium</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Medium-Fast</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: Medium * Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Vengeance: Increases damage based off missing health, higher tiers increase damage more</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Sharpness enchant doesn't stack with vengeance, whichever offers the highest damage will be used</span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Crowbill:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uGLy9gl.png\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: Medium</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Medium</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: Medium * Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Crippling: Inflicts Slowness for 1s</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Armor Piercing: Increased damage to armored entities</span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Katana:</strong></span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EIipFON.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Damage: Medium</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Speed: Medium</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Attack Range: Medium * Better Combat Stat</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*Moxie: Increases attack speed every hit</span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>WIP Weapons:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>*These weapons may not be added to the mod, nothing is final</em></span></p>\n<br />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Claws</strong> - low damage, hitting entities gives temporary small speed boost, each hit increases speed boost more (will be capped). </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">One handed</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Twin Blades</strong> - medium damage, killing entities gives a small damage buff, if another entity is killed quickly after, the damage buff will be increased</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>War Axe&nbsp;</strong>- medium-high damage, damage bypasses shields and is unaffected by potion effects, hitting the same entity multiple times will inflict bleed</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;All effects are subject to change, if you have any ideas or thoughts then let me know!</span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Compatability</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-combat-by-daedelus\">Better Combat</a> - all weapons make use of the animations and stats added by the better combat mod</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/simple-corinthium\">Simple Corinthium</a> - adds corinthium versions of all weapons</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ogfTkBm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/oreganized\">Oreganized</a> - adds electrum versions of all weapons</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4O10gxV.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"78\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/oh-the-biomes-youll-go\">Oh The Biomes You'll Go</a> - adds pendorite versions of all weapons</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A5IQZFJ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"78\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deeperdarker\">Deeper and Darker</a> - adds warden versions of all weapons</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CedGhpK.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"78\" /></p>\n<p>This mod is 1.19.2 only</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enlightened-end\">Enlightened End</a> - adds adamantite versions of all weapons</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/71G15Z0.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"78\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/the-twilight-forest\">Twilight Forest</a> - adds ironwood, steeleaf, knightmetal, and fiery versions of all weapons</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5ZCCQS5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3zlCG7a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A2ERkx9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y5gLbdA.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Compat to do list:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">I plan on adding compatability for every popular mod that adds a tool set.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Current to do list:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Stalwart Dungeons</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Blue Skies</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Aquaculture 2</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Buddy Cards&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Upgraded Netherite</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Forbidden and Arcanus</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Majrusz's Progressive Difficulty</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LieonLion's Enderite</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Plus the End</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Create Addons (Alloyed,&nbsp;Stuff &amp; Additions)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Enderite Mod</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Copper Armor &amp; Tools</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Spirit</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">End's Phantasm</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Frosted Friends</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Additional Additions</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If there is a mod you want me to add compat with that isn't on the list, just let me know.</span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>FAQ</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Can you update to the newest version?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Yes, but updates take time and will be done when I have time to do them</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Can you downgrade to X version?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- No, 1.18.2 is the lowest supported version</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Can you add X weapon?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Maybe. The criteria is it has to add something unique or interesting or fill a gap</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Can you add compatability with X mod?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Most likely yes, don't expect it to be quick though</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Does this work without Better Combat?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Yes, however it may be unbalanced</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Can I use this mod in my modpack?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Yes</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Check out my other mods:</strong></span></p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/simple-corinthium\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1fS6nzK.png\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/simple-enchantments\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d1vkzqv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/difficult-spawners\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c7OCwgw.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/simple-bracers\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fDC31Ym.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stratum\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/71BbR50.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/revised-phantoms\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DPgZLAI.png\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" /></a></span></p>",
